{"tid":2324312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍店求變｜富臨「一劏三」開西式café和風凍肉店","createTime":"2020-12-14T00:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T17:00:26.000Z","uid":41343,"like":17,"dislike":191,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"072d40de24b024e74b44d12eb281820645d8ee7f","tid":2324312,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201214/CJ7STMOQQVCNPAQQNH2YSYKX4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201214%2FCJ7STMOQQVCNPAQQNH2YSYKX4E%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725DbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=02c789a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201214%2FCJ7STMOQQVCNPAQQNH2YSYKX4E%2F&h=23479ae8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201214/CJ7STMOQQVCNPAQQNH2YSYKX4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》發現，近月公司不斷分拆現有酒樓舖位轉做其他用途，包括「吉田食品超市」、「PHI」，以新品牌示人欲「 搣甩」藍店味，在最新業績及官網都沒有披露。"},{"pid":"23ec55d575b9639f9a7a85662f96234392b7ca58","tid":2324312,"uid":41343,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:20:44.000Z","msg":"平賣「廚師腸」吸師奶客<br />\n「吉田」至自今年初已開設5間分店，分別為於將軍澳、黃大仙、美孚、屯門及沙田。記者曾到各區的分店查看，發現將軍澳，以中產客為主的PopCorn分店設於日式火鍋店「大將」（同為富臨集團旗下）旁，採高檔日式裝潢，但設「今日特價產品」，如38元黑椒豬手、25元雪藏排骨等，由於價錢與商場定位存落差，吸引大批主婦上前選購。<br />\n<br />\n記者亦曾在屯門「吉田」首間分店查詢，該店為於街市中心，傍晚時間人流暢旺。職員在門外叫賣雪藏「熟雞」及「廚師腸」，其中「廚師腸」售12.5元一包，比隔鄰舖13.4元平。現場所見，近九成的顧客都是購買廚師腸，其餘物品乏人問津。"},{"pid":"22b2cb0bb98e721228bb005120f2bdcb13895d0c","tid":2324312,"uid":41343,"like":70,"dislike":4,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:21:30.000Z","msg":"早前示威現場美孚分店，記者發現早前職工盟示威的接待樓層，已將一半改為建成「PHI COFFEE &amp; PANCAKE」咖啡店，甫開店即在Openrice獲得不少正評，如「顏值滿分嘅pancake」、「美孚的小確幸」。店內定位與區內另一間被視為「黃店」的The Planet十分相似。而酒樓一樓部份位置則分拆為吉田售賣凍肉。<br />\n<br />\n剛開業的PHI及吉田門外都擺滿了慶祝開店花籃，但母公司富臨卻「意外地」沒有送上。由於「吉田」的招標用上白底藍字日式風格，有網友在官方Facebook專頁查詢「同一田有無關係？」但被其他網友識破：「同富臨最有關係」，之後專頁就沒有再更新。"},{"pid":"87355d8f2733483fa59874534d1c8d6121bb3c6a","tid":2324312,"uid":18477,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">@終極黃藍地圖</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f5b409d0deb05366d6a212479c2e33f628ec517c","tid":2324312,"uid":103230,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:21:52.000Z","msg":"見到富臨又諗起當日班鄉黑入去換衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e35bcc805fd6dbf7a549ca44ecdf7c6d92e3ff","tid":2324312,"uid":48026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d964048c5fd9f060e78dc122b25df3e2ef6db339","tid":2324312,"uid":24660,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:23:49.000Z","msg":"中国人改晒啲日本名做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65398e42369cd78968fcd5e20bdc5651cd6d6a5a","tid":2324312,"uid":104804,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"邊個光顧=支持黑社會"},{"pid":"e41575a5a4ae14fa878c1d56a2bb2b64a2b2cfa4","tid":2324312,"uid":34410,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"87355d8f2733483fa59874534d1c8d6121bb3c6a","tid":2324312,"uid":18477,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">@終極黃藍地圖</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:24:48.000Z","msg":"自己入form報料啦"},{"pid":"2004cf4a7f9d49a7051e2e28e9d64da41cf84ebd","tid":2324312,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202941942221ada3c65bdd606afce5192bd5c861","tid":2324312,"uid":243677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:31:46.000Z","msg":"標簽藍店 唔可以停<img