":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:51:14.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》翻查部份上市被網民稱為「藍店」年初至今的表現，其中合興（47，持有香港吉野家經營權）累計跌52%、翠華（1314）累計跌34%、太興（6811）跌14%。<br />\n<br />\n其中合興的中期報告顯示的收入以中國市場為主，盈轉虧蝕6,623萬元人民幣，公司並沒有獨立提及香港市場<br />\n<br />\n個記者應該柒左<br />\n合興上巿果部份唔包吉野家香港業務<br />\n緊係唔提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4faba44eddbb602b58b9c492b2741d3c390103f","tid":2324312,"uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGLrVNY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGLrVNY.png&h=658a7bab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjuDMUE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjuDMUE.png&h=e3269b90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa3863ed7026f928c00454a3613379abbb22a58","tid":2324312,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"87355d8f2733483fa59874534d1c8d6121bb3c6a","tid":2324312,"uid":18477,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">@終極黃藍地圖</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:57:18.000Z","msg":"仲有 和你FC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/fcwithyou/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Ffcwithyou%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725DbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=1fef3776\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/fcwithyou/</a>"},{"pid":"5223f75ab37e714367ae14f0d5d133ba6f015fe3","tid":2324312,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08473e38fe140f0efa934a64b175222cf6d2003","tid":23243